I can’t really say with certainty how oppressive Riven top is to face, since I don’t play ranked, though the forums have been abuzz with threads on her strength for quite awhile now. She may be due for some tweaking but calling the balance team and developers of the game liars is not the best approach if you want to get you’re point across...

I fully expect to get downvoted for this comment so have at it.

